ission of Lorelei Bennett or at the dictate of the Revenant Prince or his Marquis, Abraham Twiggs.%0a%0ahttp://imageshack.us/a/img35/8530/0mdj.jpg http://imageshack.us/a/img822/7487/c98l.jpg%0a%0a'''Resonance:''' Historic\\%0a'''Territory:''' [[Players/Lorelei Bennett]], Isle of Hope Regent: [[Players/Abraham Twiggs]]%0a[[#locationend]]%0a%0a----%0a(:include CityBook.Directory:)
